146
00:07:32,118 --> 00:07:33,244
<font color="japanese">フフッ</font>

147
00:07:33,327 --> 00:07:35,538
<font color="japanese">ま… まあ
そんな むげになんて…</font>

148
00:07:35,621 --> 00:07:36,831
<font color="japanese">そうですわ</font>

149
00:07:36,914 --> 00:07:38,082
<font color="japanese">私たちは そんな…</font>

